    Name box ☰ Identifies the selected → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range/cell, chart item or drawing object; positioned at the left side of the *formula bar*. Allows to name a cell or a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range[range].
    Row and column headings ☰ The gray (numbered or lettered) area to the top and left of a row or column. An entire row/column can be selected by clicking on the heading, the width/height of the columns/rows can be changed there as well.
    Sheet tabs ☰
    → Microsoft/Office/GUI/title-bar[Title bar] ☰ At the top of the Excel window, displays the name of the → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Workbook currently worked on.
